headline: Niagen Bioscience And Two Other High Growth Stocks With Strong Insider Ownership
summary: In the last week, the United States market has stayed flat, but over the past 12 months, it has risen by 17%, with earnings forecast to grow by 15% annually. In this context of steady growth, stocks like Niagen Bioscience and others with high insider ownership can be appealing as they often indicate confidence from those closest to the company in its potential for future success.
